<div class=" zm-editable-content clearfix">你要战，我便战。<br><br>古人讲“敢同冰桶争高下，不向微笑让寸分”，就是要有这种精神。<br><br><noscript><img src="//pic4.zhimg.com/5d61f993b4540ef0d935d211429905c3_b.jpg" data-rawwidth="720" data-rawheight="1280" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb" width="720" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/5d61f993b4540ef0d935d211429905c3_r.jpg"></noscript><img src="//s1.zhimg.com/misc/whitedot.jpg" data-rawwidth="720" data-rawheight="1280" class="origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy" width="720" data-original="//pic4.zhimg.com/5d61f993b4540ef0d935d211429905c3_r.jpg" data-actualsrc="//pic4.zhimg.com/5d61f993b4540ef0d935d211429905c3_b.jpg">


